text: This text appears to be a list of download links and magnets for the movie "Killers of the Flower Moon." The links include various resolutions, codecs, and subtitle options. Some are embedded with Chinese or multiple subtitles. Users can choose the one that suits their needs best. Additionally, there is an invitation to follow the public account "影的后花园" on WeChat by scanning a provided QR code or searching for it using the ID "BluFilm."
